T1  - The Changing International Transmission of Financial Shocks: Evidence from a Classical Time-Varying FAVAR
AU  - ABBATE, ANGELA
AU  - EICKMEIER, SANDRA
AU  - LEMKE, WOLFGANG
AU  - MARCELLINO, MASSIMILIANO
